              = f (y + x)                      by GroupHomo_def
              = f #0                           by above
              = s.sum.id                       by 5.
       The second is: kernel f r.sum s.sum SUBSET R
       True by kernel_def.
   (2) x IN kernel f r.sum s.sum /\ y IN R ==> x * y IN kernel f r.sum s.sum
       This reduces to 2 subgoals:
